{"tid":2289620,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本港失業率維持6.4%　政府稱就業情況呈穩定跡象","createTime":"2020-11-17T11:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T18:28:13.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"5037669e7ffcd5d11ced958b6f26d4684f62815d","tid":2289620,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:13:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560452-20201117.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560452-20201117.htm&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM42qRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=c558fee7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560452-20201117.htm&h=00acf611\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560452-20201117.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n本港最新失業率為 6.4%，與上次公布的數字相同。<br />\n<br />\n政府公布，8月至10月經季節性調整的失業率為6.4%，與7月至9月的數字相同，其中與消費及旅遊相關行業合計的失業率下跌0.5個百分點至11.2%，當中的餐飲服務活動業下跌0.4個百分點至14.8%。運輸業的失業率則急升0.6個百分點至6.2%，為接近17年來的高位。<br />\n<br />\n在8月至10月，就業不足率維持在3.8%，總就業人數及失業人數分別較7月至9月多2900人及減少2000人。<br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局局長羅致光表示，勞工市場情況仍然困難，雖然整體經濟最近數月有一些改善，但僱主招聘意欲應該依然審慎，尤其經濟前景仍受正在變化的疫情所困擾，勞工市場短期內仍面對壓力。"},{"pid":"740d3d93cbde847df908e52aac4e45c331ecd9ff","tid":2289620,"uid":50386,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:16:17.000Z","msg":"國泰炒咗五千人都冇變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假唔假啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1034d8310f906e30d43b351738d465bc7f6586d9","tid":2289620,"uid":70786,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"740d3d93cbde847df908e52aac4e45c331ecd9ff","tid":2289620,"uid":50386,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:16:17.000Z","msg":"國泰炒咗五千人都冇變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假唔假啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2